name: SeniorProject
body:
### Welcome to the Senior Design Project Page for Team Vermillion This page will be updated soon with a summary of our project. For now, everything that we are working on will be uploaded to GitHub so that there is a central repository of all of our work. This will include papers and instructions on how to use our code. Please visit the repository to learn more. --- ### Updates **24 June 2012** - At this point our project is completed and we are no longer actively maintaining this project. However, if you have questions, you can feel free to contact me (@hwrdprkns) through GitHub or email. **11 May 2012** - Project satisfactorily working. Moving on to document the code and clean up our project. --- ### Authors and Contributors
Taylor Perkins (@hwrdprkns) Weiyi "Edward" Zheng (@zhengwy888)
Farhan Shaukat Yorman Garcia
### Support or Contact Contact one of the team members through GitHub or Tufts University.
